    "body": "## Problem:\r\nNested workspace capabilities like workspace.fileOperations.didCreate and workspace.textDocumentContent are not handled consistently for dynamic and static registration provider lookup.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\nGenerate explicit registration-provider mappings from the LSP metadata and use them when registering and querying capabilities. Add coverage for dynamic and static nested workspace registrations.\r\n\r\nAI-assisted: OpenCode\r\n\r\nUnblocks: \r\n- #39526\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-05-05T20:36:02Z",
