        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> This is getting complex, thanks for continuing to refine it. Hopefully it can be simplified later.\r\n> \r\n> Is there anything to say about this in news.txt?\r\n\r\nNothing specific for this kind of stuff. This is just \"more robust handling of all the possible permutations in the spec of different providers and registration methods\". The standard isn't that \"standard\" in a lot of places.\r\n\r\nThe workspace stuff didn't matter so much before, as we didn't support any of the methods nested within it, which only came to light when I started looking at `workspace/textDocumentContent`\r\n\r\nI'm hoping the expanded test suite will allow for a \"fearless\" refactor of this in the future.",
